MECM
types of servers:
CAS - central administration site
Primary Server
MP - Management Point - provides policy 
DP - Distribution Point - contains updates, OS image, boot image, software packages and updates

Deployment types:
Available - not installed on WS directly, must go to software center
Required - Software is installed no user input required, deadline set by admins

Pilot - collection of machines to test software deployment before deployment to enterprise

Software testing WS(workstation) - after pilot, this is the test subject












